data.description: This is that rare, one of a kind horse property with water rights! Adorable ranch home, just waiting for the right owner. Plenty of room for horses, dogs, RV's, campers, trailers and desert toys. Shaded dog run, hay barn, and plenty more. Check it out, see for yourself. New pump house with overhead storage. Detached building, insulated with some plumbing, many opportunities for this great space. Outside city limits, just off the Reno Hwy. 28-4 rail panels, 8 gates and 3 shelters stay with property. Sellers are motivated!!!  They are offering a $5,000 credit to the buyers for assistance in closing costs or buy down interest!
